{"tid":988873,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"愛得太遲呢首歌真係會聽到喊","createTime":"2019-01-20T12:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T06:17:54.000Z","uid":85460,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56837f77cd907476af2bfa918616726fada46ffd","tid":988873,"uid":85460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"人愈大 聽起上黎就愈大感觸<br />\n友情家人工作愛情 句句都寫到入肉..<br />\n呢排做野好忙日日自己一個人 一聽到就忍唔住<br />\n<br />\n友情:<br />\n各也紮職以後　沒法暢聚<br />\n而終於相約到　但無言共對　疏淡如水<br />\n家人:<br />\n日夜做　見爸爸　剛好想呻<br />\n卻霎眼　看出他　多了皺紋<br />\n而他的蒼老感　是從來未覺　太內疚擔心<br />\n工作:<br />\n盲目地發奮　忙忙忙其實自私<br />\n夢中也習慣　有壓力要我得志<br />\n愛情:<br />\n要抱要吻要怎麼也好<br />\n不要相信一切有下次<br />\n相擁我所愛又花幾多秒　這幾秒"},{"pid":"23f642e112b6382601d860f0a84188209d9d01c5","tid":988873,"uid":121247,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"恒大 我讀得好開心"},{"pid":"49d9bfe70203e289613dfffeefe84a955ef870c1","tid":988873,"uid":81256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbab5a7d74012c26b14007d49926d7a32e5ce349","tid":988873,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b832fd487174250205c6dfb248e3ddd0e0b176","tid":988873,"uid":10269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"要抱要吻要怎麼也好<br />\n不要相信一切有下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367586ba3ab4fe3763321ec2db3ee47d9406c802","tid":988873,"uid":12591,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:49:02.000Z","m